I checked the nameplate of the apartment and dashed up the stairs, inserting the key I'd insisted the real estate agent give me into the door of the intended room.[l][r]

[_tb_end_text]

[playse  volume="100"  time="1000"  buf="0"  storage="lockopen.ogg"  ]
