The room was completely silent.[l][r]

I pressed the light switch, but no light turned on. I couldn't tell if the breaker was off or if the electricity had been cut off.[l][r]
However, it wasn't dark yet. As I walked further into the room and opened the curtains, the sunlight that poured in illuminated the room.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

