On the bathroom sink amidst scattered towels and undergarments, a dull mirror reflected light in a murky fashion. Looking closer, the dirt spelled out words.[l][r]
They were hastily written words, possibly with lip balm or something similar. What is this, some old song? I traced the clumsy letters with my eyes.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[cm  ]
[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
'Sorry if we caused any trouble. But, thank you.'[l][r]

"No, you did well, Yuri. Nicely done."[l][r]
Beyond the letters, I saw my own lips curling up in a slight smile.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

